        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='11518' id='9' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='63450' x='17705' y='-916'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>当我们将目光从宏观流派拉近到微观艺人时，发现了一个极其有趣的现象：</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>顶流艺人的热度轨迹，正是流派繁荣的完美镜像。</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Taylor Swift </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>以 10.80K 的 Track 计数和 16,074.55M 的恐怖粉丝量，成为了</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Pop 乐</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>无可争议的代言人。 </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Bad Bunny </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>以 5.281.79M 的粉丝量，引领着 </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Latin（拉丁乐） </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>在全球流媒体上的文化逆袭。 </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Drake </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>与 </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>Playboi Carti </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>则高高伫立在 </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>HipHop </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>的山巅。 </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='3927' id='13' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='28951' x='33435' y='11780'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='华文中宋' fontsize='11'>那么大家为什么喜欢听这些歌？有没有一个黄金公式呢？</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Microsoft YaHei' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{E2489115-2541-4170-9F1E-7046FF790B5E}' />
    </dashboard>
